products.title: Air Jordan 1 High OG phantom
products.description: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG phantom: Supplied by a premier sneaker marketplace dealing with unworn, already sold out, in demand rarities. Each product is rigorously inspected by experienced experts guaranteeing authenticity. The Air Jordan 1 High OG “Phantom” is another outstanding look for Michael Jordan’s first signature shoe. The unique construction for the iconic silhouette features a “crinkled” leather base in Sail with Phantom (light grey) leather overlays and University Red accents on the contrast stitching and double Swoosh. The sole unit matches the Sail color on the upper. Metal lace grommets add another unique touch to this colorway, while black details for the “wings” Air Jordan logo and Nike Air logo on the tongue complete the clean look. The Air Jordan 1 High OG “Phantom” released in March 2019.

products.title: Air Jordan 1 Mid unc
products.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid UNC draws inspiration from Michael Jordan’s alma mater for a fresh new look on the mid-top silhouette. The famous University Blue of the University of North Carolina shines bright on this eye-pleasing colorway of the Jordan 1 Mid with the color covering the Swooshes and collar. A white leather base spans the perforated toe, mid-panel and heel. Additional hits of Carolina Blue can be found on the Wings logo on the collar and Jumpman branding on the white nylon tongue tab. Jordan Brand opts for an always classy white rubber midsole and contrasting light blue outsole to finish off the styling of the shoe. The Air Jordan 1 Mid “UNC” was released on January 14, 2020.

products.title: Adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2
products.description: Get your hands on the latest offering from Kanye West’s highly sought-after sneaker collection. The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 silhouette is updated here in a new colourway dubbed “Fade”, consisting of an earthy brown Primeknit upper. Placed atop a signature Boost midsole for comfort, the low-top pair are finished with a blue monofilament side stripe to break up the look. Don’t pass up on these.
